ed line-of-sight\nradiative transfer simulations confirm these expectations and predict a rich\nthermal structure in the IGM during HeII reionisation. [Abridged]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Jul 2008 13:44:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Jan 2009 14:39:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 16 Mar 2009 11:25:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
