t cluster could be related to fact\nthat these objects have very late spectral types compared to the solar-type\nstars in other cluster studies. Finally, the optical spectroscopy reveals that\none of the X-ray sources is produced by a Herbig Haro object in the cloud.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Jul 2008 07:08:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
